descriptionNullable:
ImageCategorizer is an intelligent image classification software designed to simplify the process of 
categorizing and labeling images. It leverages deep learning technology to automatically assign labels to images 
based on pre-trained models. The software provides an intuitive graphical user interface (GUI) for users to load 
models, set class names, and classify images.
 **Paper: **Shuvo Kumar Basak. (2023). ImageCategorizer: Intelligent Image Classification Softwar. Zenodo. https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8387206
**GitHub:** https://github.com/shuvobasak4004/ImageCategorizer-Intelligent-Image-Classification-Software
